arch 1993}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary=The absence of a murder weapon complicates the investigation into the murder of a drug addict who stole from her family to support her habit.\n |LineColor=000000\n}}{{#invoke:Episode list|sublist|Law & Order (season 3)\n |EpisodeNumber=60\n |EpisodeNumber2=16\n |Title=Jurisdiction\n |DirectedBy=[[Bruce Seth Green]]\n |WrittenBy=Walon Green & Ren\u00e9 Balcer\n |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|1993|3|3}}\n |ProdCode=68017\n |Aux4=\n |ShortSummary=Stone battles the Brooklyn D.A.'s office over prosecutorial jurisdiction in the case of a mentally handicapped man who confesses to the stabbing deaths of two women.\n |LineColor=000000\n}}{{#invoke:Episode list|sublist|Law & Order (season 3)\n |EpisodeNumber=61\n |EpisodeNumber2=17\n |Title=Conduct Unbecoming\n |DirectedBy=Arthur W. Forney\n |WrittenBy={{StoryTeleplay\n | s = Walon Green & Peter S. Greenberg;\n | t = Michael S. Chernuchin & Ren\u00e9 Balcer\n | slabel = {{abbr|S|Story by}}\n | tlabel = {{abbr|T|Teleplay by}}\n }}\n |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|1993|3|10}}\n |ProdCode=68023\n |Aux4=13.50<ref>{{cite news |last1=Gable |first1=Donna |last2=Daniels |first2=Charlene |title=ABC improves with bench strength |date=17 March 1993 |work=USA TODAY}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary=Stone and the police battle the closed ranks of the Navy to investigate the death of a female Naval officer during a party in a Manhattan hotel.\n* Based on the 1991 [[Tailhook scandal]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://tv.yahoo.com/photos/stars-on-law-order-before-their-big-break-slideshow/julianna-margulies-93-conduct-unbecoming-photo-1346283357.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2013-07-15 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120906054600/http://tv.yahoo.com/photos/stars-on-law-order-before-their-big-break-slideshow/julianna-margulies-93-conduct-unbecoming-photo-1346283357.html |archivedate=2012-09-06 }}</ref>\n |LineColor=000000\n}}{{#invoke:Episode list|sublist|Law & Order (season 3)\n |EpisodeNumb